The species is very close to 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Araceae" genus="E." kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="E. neorepanda" order="Diptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="67134" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="neorepanda">
